body_html:
Hi,

Thanks for filing and apologies for the delay in response. This was fixed with f12b843. You should be able to see correct edge shapes (not only the first output shape) in the 0.9 release, or if you don't want to wait, we just published a release candidate https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/releases/tag/v0.9.0rc0

Thanks for filing and apologies for the delay in response. This was fixed with f12b843d78b0119b3f8d0ffc99a9e417d9232e7c.
